  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个预约系统的状态流转图。用户从创建预约开始，先进入草稿状态，提交后变成待审核，这时候系统要发邮件通知用户和管理员。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Draft",
        "Pending",
        "email notification"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是用户开始创建预约。那Pending之后呢？管理员可以批准或者拒绝吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Confirmed",
        "Rejected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Pending可以转到Confirmed或Rejected。如果确认了，等到开始时间用户签到就进入InProgress，这时候要锁定资源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
        "Confirmed",
        "Rejected",
        "InProgress",
        "resources locked"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：草稿→提交→待审核→确认→进行中，同时加上拒绝的分支。进行中状态我标注资源锁定。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Draft",
        "Pending",
        "Confirmed",
        "InProgress",
        "Rejected",
        "resources locked"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有几个终止场景。Confirmed状态下用户可以提前取消；如果到点开始时间没签到，要算NoShow；进行中也可以紧急取消。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Confirmed",
        "Cancelled",
        "NoShow",
        "InProgress",
        "emergency cancellation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "收到。那Completed是什么情况？是正常结束吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Completed",
        "InProgress"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，InProgress到结束时间就Completed。Completed、Cancelled、Rejected、NoShow都是终态，回到结束节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "InProgress",
        "Completed",
        "Cancelled",
        "Rejected",
        "NoShow",
        "end state"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了。Pending旁边我加了注释说明发邮件通知，InProgress旁边标注资源锁定，所有终态都连到结束节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Pending",
